,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"但要留意番, 催淚彈平射, <br />\n對住人個頭同身都係好危險"},{"pid":"f4abc7fc9834c1674c2430626934181169ad3aab","tid":1416851,"uid":6446,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5_0FVGtug0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5_0FVGtug0&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d32df4e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5_0FVGtug0</a>"},{"pid":"6bf047075a8ebb08d54de5b66036528c7208463b","tid":1416851,"uid":45334,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"唔該大家唔好因為放得多就習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，催淚氣體經由催淚彈殼爆炸散發，如果爆炸接近人身則可導致爆炸傷害。一份2011年的研究指出，在18個由催淚彈殼爆炸造成的嚴重血管傷害個案中，大部份都需動手術醫治，其中3個個案需要截肢。<br />\n<br />\n第二，催淚氣體可被吸入肺部和而胡椒噴霧一般只停留在皮膚表面。2002年已有研究指出催淚氣體導致的急性嚴重缺氧可達須留醫深切治療部的嚴重程度。一份2004年的研究指出對催淚氣體的敏感反應亦包括咽喉收窄、支氣管收窄，對哮喘病人或需以全身麻醉（以醫治其他同時受到的傷害）者尤其危險。2014年研究93個多次受催淚氣體傷害的個案顯示其長遠併發症包括慢性支氣管炎及肺活量下降。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1026922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1026922&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=857fcd1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1026922&h=858b0c7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1026922</a>"},{"pid":"b56437cc47b5b9e7163cb7125f25e90a3f1d3645","tid":1416851,"uid":152063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4abc7fc9834c1674c2430626934181169ad3aab","tid":1416851,"uid":6446,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5_0FVGtug0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5_0FVGtug0&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d32df4e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5_0FVGtug0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打補source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8900370bb88796c662f1a96146b56a4241fb6110","tid":1416851,"uid":293698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02b66227c8dfb21b3126032ce4f1f0511c0e2d08","tid":1416851,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd1e04139d189539295247e9eb233ab7fc86f1dc","tid":1416851,"uid":62749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8900370bb88796c662f1a96146b56a4241fb6110","tid":1416851,"uid":293698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a4587834b276c077eba5d9af711e62115d68208","tid":1416851,"uid":62749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bb4028c0953c939644988536c389864c82bff1bd","tid":1416851,"uid":293698,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"但要留意番, 催淚彈平射, <br />\n對住人個頭同身都係好危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"同埋唔好學沙田咁樣圍捕囉, 係驅散就驅散"},{"pid":"1bddce18aa3490faedcabe77c828b75dda4d6e45","tid":1416851,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e56bb5e73b31a5a0bfd894d9231b785e0f7b053","tid":1416851,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb4028c0953c939644988536c389864c82bff1bd","tid":1416851,"uid":293698,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"阿伯好波 難得"}]}